HEAT cheeseburgers as directed on package. MEANWHILE, cook and stir onion in 1 tsp. of the oil in nonstick skillet on medium-high heat until tender. Remove onion from skillet. ADD remaining 1 tsp. oil and mushrooms to skillet; cook until lightly browned, turning occasionally. Add onion and vinegar; mix lightly. PLACE cheeseburger on bottom half of each bagel; top with arugula and mushroom mixture. Season with pepper to taste. Cover with remaining bagel halves.